{"tid":1629883,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"估計出左45000警力/以後唔再游行","createTime":"2019-10-06T10:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:32:00.000Z","uid":130502,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1d4648e95e3ba98b79ddcb3aa1951c79592c0a","tid":1629883,"uid":130502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:47:36.000Z","msg":"尋日休息就係為左今日大圍捕<br />\n<br />\n30000警察加15000公安同解放軍<br />\n<br />\n因為示威者居然今日咁傻集中埋一齊游行 <br />\n<br />\n只要封鎖逃走路線加設rb上車捉人<br />\n<br />\n根本係清理示威者既最佳時機<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以後強烈建議咪撚再集會，根本係送頭，只可以持續玩18區游擊<br />\n<br />\n乜撚民陣同文宣咪撚再提呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n否則d人好快拉鳩晒，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只有警察會想見到示威者集中埋一齊</span><br />\n<br />\n拉鳩晒之後藍絲，港共，黑社會同被裝修既鋪好快就會出黎報復<br />\n<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"6086d0f059827f6a899f9a1f17aa374e3ec8fc77","tid":1629883,"uid":299104,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eJKVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eJKVS.png&h=fd892c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GobPu5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGobPu5a.jpg&h=8c19a255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=zkxump%2FGNOlz%2FwmZAqM4lOgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=f1e6c0d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I</a>"},{"pid":"5040a5dc4edfee05916afc459edf263ec3ec6bf1","tid":1629883,"uid":130502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:48:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1ca9e8e734bf8199de8d559ba22e36acfec90cda","tid":1629883,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited